  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Qsite Ticket Status is a RepairQ companion that allows your customers to check the progress of their repair or service tickets. With this feature, customers can stay informed about their ticket status, view any notes added by your team, check their pending balance, and access store contact information\u2014all without needing to contact your store directly. Qsite Ticket Status is available for all subscription tiers.</p><ul><li><p>Reduce incoming calls and inquiries about ticket status.</p></li><li><p>Enhance customer experience by providing instant access to real-time updates.</p></li><li><p>Increase engagement with your business through an easy-to-use tracking tool.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-HowDoCustomersViewQsiteTicketStatus?\">How Do Customers View Qsite Ticket Status?</h3><p>If your URL is &quot;https://businessname.repairq.io&quot;, the Qsite Ticket Status page will be &quot;https://businessname.repairq.io<strong>/t</strong>&quot;. Customers can visit the Status Tracker URL from any browser. By entering their Ticket Number and Last Name, they can instantly view their ticket details. Customers can receive this link in multiple ways:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Receipts</strong> - Customers can receive a link to the Qsite Status page on their receipts. You have the option to print:</p><ul><li><p>The <strong>URL</strong>, which customers can enter into their browser.</p></li><li><p>A <strong>QR Code</strong>, which customers scan and access their ticket status instantly on their smart device.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Automated Notifications</strong> - Customers can receive<strong> </strong>email and SMS notifications that include a direct link to the Qsite Status page.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936851011/Add+a+Qsite+Ticket+Status+Link+to+Receipts+and+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936851011\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Add a Qsite\u2122 Ticket Status Link to Receipts</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936588905/Qsite+Opportunities\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936588905\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qsite\u2122 Opportunities</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523327/Qsite+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523327\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qsite\u2122 Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936982118/RepairQ+API+-+Embed+Qsite+Ticket+Status+Into+Your+Website\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936982118\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Embed Qsite\u2122 Ticket Status Into Your Website via RepairQ APIs</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246478\" rel=\"nofollow\">Getting Started: Automated Notifications</a></p></li></ul><h2 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-inline\" alt=\"Technical - 124a6d.png\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/Technical%20-%20124a6d.png?api=v2\"></span> </h2><h2 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-QsiteTicketStatus\">Qsite Ticket Status</h2><p>If your URL is &quot;https://businessname.repairq.io&quot;, the Qsite Ticket Status page will be &quot;https://businessname.repairq.io<strong>/t</strong>&quot;. Customers can navigate to this URL on any browser, enter their Ticket Number and Last Name, and view available ticket details.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183258.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183303.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-URLandQRCodesonTickets\">URL and QR Codes on Tickets</h2><p>Use <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932361958\" rel=\"nofollow\">Print Template Settings</a> to print out the full link and/or a QR Code on receipts for users to scan with their smart device and navigate directly to the status page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183310.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183316.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><h2 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-SendaTicketStatusLinkviaAutomatedNotifications\">Send a Ticket Status Link via Automated Notifications</h2><p>Managers can create an <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246478\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notification</a> that can include a link to the Qsite Ticket Status page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183322.png?api=v2\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"Qsite\u2122TicketStatus-KeepCustomersUpdatedonTheirTickets-QsiteTicketStatusFeatures\">Qsite Ticket Status Features</h2><p>The Qsite Ticket Status page shows a ticket summary, including the current status, any balance due, and the last time the ticket was updated.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183329.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The Notes tab on the left column shows any customer-visible notes on the ticket. Notes that are visible to customers must be marked as such on the ticket.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183334.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The lower-left section of the status window includes your store details with links to call the store or view directions to your location. This information can be updated in your Location Information settings.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936425067/image-20230607-183339.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.22.X</p>",
